data.title: American Health Network, part of Optum
data.meta_description: American Health Network is a large physician group practice driven to provide high-quality, cost-effective exceptional care to our patients in Ohio and Indiana.
data.text:
Healthier care for a better life

American Health Network is part of Optum. At Optum, we’re a family of primary care providers, specialists and care teams focused on keeping you healthy. Learn more about Optum.

At Optum Primary and Specialty Care, our doctors and care teams work hard to help keep you healthy. We don’t just care for you when you’re sick. We’re here to partner with you to help you reach your personal health goals.
